===簽證===
:參見：[[韓國簽證政策|韓國簽證政策]]和[[韓國公民簽證要求|韓國公民簽證要求]]
:以及：[[巴西簽證政策|巴西簽證政策]]和[[巴西公民簽證要求|巴西公民簽證要求]]

两国相互免签证，自2002年5月20日起，持[[韓國護照|韓國護照]]的[[韓國人|韓國公民]]可以免簽證的方式入境[[巴西|巴西]]，停留最多90日。<ref>[http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/decreto/2002/D4235.htm Decree no. 4235] {{Wayback|url=http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/decreto/2002/D4235.htm |date=20090113052747 }}, 巴西总统府. {{in lang|pt}}</ref>自同日起，持[[巴西护照|巴西护照]]的[[巴西人口|巴西公民]]也可以免簽證的方式入境[[韓國|韓國]]，停留最多90日。

此外，兩國每年皆提供特定名額的18－30歲青年為期1年的[[工作假期签证|度假打工簽證]]，最多停留2年。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://whic.mofa.go.kr/upload/temp/kr_workingholiday_english.pdf|title=Korea Working Holiday 2014|access-date=2022-03-15|archive-date=2022-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220125064219/https://whic.mofa.go.kr/upload/temp/kr_workingholiday_english.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://whic.mofa.go.kr/contents.do?menuNo=90&contentsNo=38|title=외교부 워킹홀리데이 인포센터-Program|last=Easymedia|website=whic.mofa.go.kr|access-date=16 December 2017|archive-date=2022-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220315050653/http://whic.mofa.go.kr/contents.do?menuNo=90&contentsNo=38}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreadaily.com/news/read.asp?art_id=7917159|title=영사서비스 이렇게 개선되었습니다!|website=미주중앙일보|access-date=2020-04-14|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925081445/http://www.koreadaily.com/news/read.asp?art_id=7917159|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.br/pt-br/pagina-inicial|title=Governo Federal - Governo do Brasil.|website=Governo do Brasil|access-date=2021-05-22|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513095057/https://www.gov.br/pt-br/pagina-inicial/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.br/mre/en/homepage|title=Homepage|website=Ministério das Relações Exteriores|access-date=2021-05-22|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522112817/https://www.gov.br/mre/en/homepage|url-status=live}}</ref>

